'''冬季會議'''（{{lang-en|Winter Meetings}}）是一個於每年12月舉行的活動。[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]30支球隊和其[[美國職棒小聯盟|小聯盟]]所屬球隊的代表集會四天，討論聯盟事務和休賽期交易，也有其他棒球相關活動如商業展覽和就業諮詢等。包括聯盟行政人員、各隊老闆、總經理、球隊球探、來自他國的參觀者、參加展覽者和希望進入美國職棒組織工作的求職者等人參與。{{sfn|Peden|2011|p=195}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/milb/events/wintermeetings.jsp|title=2014 Baseball Winter Meetings returns to San Diego after three decades|publisher=Minor League Baseball|year=2014|accessdate=18 January 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108094141/http://www.milb.com/milb/events/wintermeetings.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2014/dec/09/major-league-baseball-winter-meetings-job-fair/|title=Baseball Jobs: Will work for peanuts|first=Jonathan|last=Horn|date=December 9, 2014|accessdate=18 January 2015|work=U-T San Diego|archive-date=2015-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150625130200/http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2014/dec/09/major-league-baseball-winter-meetings-job-fair/|dead-url=no}}</ref>會議最後一天，沒有被列入球隊40人名單的球員可在[[規則五選秀|規則五選秀]]中被其他球隊選中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2014/12/2014-rule-5-draft-results.html|title=2014 Rule 5 Draft Results|first=Zach|last=Links|date=11 December 2014|accessdate=11 December 2014|work=MLB Trade Rumors|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111224531/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2014/12/2014-rule-5-draft-results.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

