==出席者==
冬季會議吸引數以千計的出席者。官方評估大約有3000人參與2014年冬季會議，這包含球隊老闆、總經理、總教練、球探、球員經紀人、律師、會計師還有各國觀光客。{{sfn|Peden|2011|p=195}}{{sfn|Solomon|Freeman|2012|p=185}}{{sfn|Gorman|2007|pp=7-8}} 一般而言，球員不會出席，但是自由球員通常會前來向各隊介紹自己。{{sfn|Solomon|Freeman|2012|p=185}}在2014年的聖地牙哥冬季會議，約有750位媒體人領有[[記者證|記者證]]。<ref name=wsj/>

晚上會有大聯盟球隊為其小聯盟附屬球隊所舉辦的歡迎會。{{sfn|Solomon|Freeman|2012|p=182}} 亦有為總教練和棒球記者準備的午餐會。<ref name=nyt/>

==球員交易和簽約==
[[File:Bill_Veeck_1964.JPG|thumb]]
[[File:BarryBonds1993.jpg|150px]]的[[貝瑞·邦茲|貝瑞·邦茲]]]]
在球隊高層齊聚一堂之下，冬季會議成為典型的球員交易和自由球員簽約的場所。{{sfn|Carroll|2007|p=78}}不過，直到20世紀末期在飯店大廳進行的非正式會議已經被簡訊和電子郵件取代。因為眾多的媒體人員和球迷的聚集在現場，大部分的高層交流改至較隱蔽的套房內。<ref name=wsj>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/mlb-winter-meetings-with-fewer-meetings-1418139567|title=Baseball's Winter Meetings—Minus the Meetings|first=Brian|last=Costa|date=9 December 2014|accessdate=18 January 2015|work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|archive-date=2017-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215144245/https://www.wsj.com/articles/mlb-winter-meetings-with-fewer-meetings-1418139567|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=nyt/> 

下列是在過去的冬季會議中較值得注意的交易和合約:
<!--請添加較為重要的項目，而不要任意列舉-->
*在1975年羅德岱堡的冬季會議，[[芝加哥白襪|芝加哥白襪隊]]的新老闆{{link-en|比爾·維克|Bill Veeck}}坐在一張飯店大廳內的桌子旁，前方有標示寫著「開放交易」(Open for Business)。會議期間他一共談成了6筆交易案，牽涉22名球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/158887650/the-best-winter-meetings-trades-of-all-time/|title=The biggest Winter Meetings trades of all time|first=AJ|last=Cassavell|year=2016|accessdate=28 January 2017|work=MLB.com|archive-date=2017-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170203205754/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/158887650/the-best-winter-meetings-trades-of-all-time/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*於1988年亞特蘭大的冬季會議，[[德克薩斯遊騎兵_(棒球)|德州遊騎兵]]商定了牽涉15名球員的3筆交易，並簽下自由球員投手[[諾蘭·萊恩|諾蘭·萊恩]]。{{sfn|Sypher|1990|p=100}}
*在1992年路易維爾的冬季會議，首度成為自由球員的[[貝瑞·邦茲|貝瑞·邦茲]]和[[舊金山巨人|舊金山巨人]]談妥一紙6年4300萬美元的合約。其中由邦茲親自洽談有關客場比賽期間能自由處置飯店套房的部分。<ref name=nyt>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/08/sports/baseball/where-baseball-is-all-the-buzz-general-managers-just-want-peace-and-quiet.html?_r=0|title=Baseball's Annual Winter Meetings Have It All, Except Quietude|first=David|last=Waldstein|date=7 December 2014|accessdate=18 January 2015|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|archive-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511081859/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/08/sports/baseball/where-baseball-is-all-the-buzz-general-managers-just-want-peace-and-quiet.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*[[艾力士·羅德里奎茲|艾力士·羅德里奎茲]]在2000年冬季會議和[[西雅圖水手|西雅圖水手]]談成一筆價值2億5200萬美元、為期10年的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/210165898/the-biggest-deals-in-winter-meetings-history/|title=Biggest free-agent deals in Winter Meetings history|first=John|last=Schlegel|date=3 December 2016|accessdate=10 February 2017|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|archive-date=2016-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206175222/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/210165898/the-biggest-deals-in-winter-meetings-history/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*2011年達拉斯冬季會議的最後一日，當年秋天隨[[聖路易紅雀|聖路易紅雀]]贏下[[世界大賽|世界大賽]]戒指的[[亞伯特·普荷斯|亞伯特·普荷斯]]與[[洛杉磯天使|洛杉磯天使]]敲定一份10年2億5000萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://espn.go.com/mlb/hotstove11/story/_/id/7330869/los-angeles-angels-shock-world-land-albert-pujols-cj-wilson|title=Angels Shock the Baseball World|first=Jayson|last=Stark|date=9 December 2011|accessdate=18 January 2015|work=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305062230/http://espn.go.com/mlb/hotstove11/story/_/id/7330869/los-angeles-angels-shock-world-land-albert-pujols-cj-wilson|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*在2014年聖地牙哥的冬季會議，經過24小時內許多的談判，[[洛杉磯道奇|洛杉磯道奇]]完成了和4支隊伍的6筆交易，關係到19位選手和1位自由球員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2014/12/11/mlb-winter-meetings-trades-dodgers-max-scherzer/20278411/|title='Aggressive' winter meetings end with many winners|first=Bob|last=Nightengale|date=12 December 2014|accessdate=18 January 2015|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|archive-date=2020-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305152629/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2014/12/11/mlb-winter-meetings-trades-dodgers-max-scherzer/20278411/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/dodgers-644986-team-year.html|title=Kemp trade is latest piece of Dodgers' reconstruction|date=11 December 2014|accessdate=18 January 2015|first=Bill|last=Plunkett|work=Orange County Register|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304140124/http://www.ocregister.com/articles/dodgers-644986-team-year.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==其他活動==
[[File:Pants-rowland.jpg|150px]]
一場大約300個攤位的商業展覽亦在冬季會議期間進行，涵蓋球具、棒球推廣和其他服務。{{sfn|Solomon|Freeman|2012|p=185}}另外一個年度活動則是職業棒球人才招募會（Professional Baseball Employment Opportunities Job Fair, PBEO Job Fair），剛投入職場的求職者選擇在此尋找工作，接受小聯盟組織的現場面試。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/chad-barr/class-is-in-session-at-th_b_2244114.html|title=Class is in Session at the Baseball Winter Meetings|first1=Chad|last1=Barr|first2=Ted|last2=Curtis|date=12 May 2012|accessdate=18 January 2015|work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|archive-date=2017-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227062347/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/chad-barr/class-is-in-session-at-th_b_2244114.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>每年大概有400至500人獲得工作，因此12月被形容為棒球界僱用的高峰。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kpbs.org/news/2014/dec/08/job-fair-baseballs-winter-meetings/|title=Baseball Executives, Jobseekers In San Diego For Winter Meetings|first=Dwane|last=Brown|date=8 December 2014|work=KPBS|accessdate=2017-02-26|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925002532/https://www.kpbs.org/news/2014/dec/08/job-fair-baseballs-winter-meetings/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自1951年起，「{{link-en|棒球之王|King of Baseball}}」頭銜在冬季會議的晚宴會被頒予一位小聯盟老將。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/awards/kingofbaseballaward.shtml|title=King of Baseball Award by Minor League Baseball|publisher=Baseball Almanac|year=2014|accessdate=18 January 2015|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627163959/https://www.baseball-almanac.com/awards/kingofbaseballaward.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另有幾個和[[美國國家棒球名人堂暨博物館|名人堂]]有關的活動：
