* 頒予為棒球廣播有傑出貢獻人士的{{link-en|福特·弗立克獎|Ford C. Frick Award}}得主公布。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://baseballhall.org/awards/ford-c-frick|title=Ford C. Frick Award|publisher=National Baseball Hall of Fame|accessdate=11 December 2014|archive-date=2014-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141122014350/http://www.baseballhall.org/awards/ford-c-frick|dead-url=no}}</ref>
